<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.223940>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Cocotanais puravida n. g., n. sp., male. A, allotype, habitus, dorsal view. B, habitus, lateral view. C, antennule. D, antenna." ;
